{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2dc1f8c674","title":"毛主席接见缅共柯生（德钦巴登顶）等谈话记录","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b3f8bd9a3c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":26,"articleId":"2dc1f8c674"}],"tags":[{"id":"29143cbd32","name":"无产阶级国际主义","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4f45e132a9","name":"贵州文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"b3c50bb47c","name":"刘宁一","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"eb87a9588f","name":"四川文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3277fff879","type":"title","text":"毛主席接见缅共柯生（德钦巴登顶）等谈话记录（未经本人审阅）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a5690cf0fa","type":"paragraph","text":"时  间：1967年11月26日17时30分至18时55分","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"57f5b03496","type":"paragraph","text":"地  点：人民大会堂湖南厅","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"296c685add","type":"paragraph","text":"参加人：缅方：柯明、罗线、何高、杨光、古方、吴明、甘底、赵明、赵云","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"afac574d4b","type":"paragraph","text":"中方：周恩来、陈伯达、康生、江青、戚本禹、姚文元、刘宁一、","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"82d0499bd1","type":"paragraph","text":"杨成武、李天佑、徐其孝、申健、成学俞、苑化冰、陈杰夫、王阳","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"013dd06d3e","type":"paragraph","text":"翻  译：陈川戈","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"dc8c0ad8f3","type":"paragraph","text":"速  记：吕辉祥","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"24b353de22","type":"paragraph","text":"（在谈话之前，毛主席接见了来到北京的缅共和罗线部队代表134人并照相。）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"19a16c5e63","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席（以下简称主席）：你们到北京有多久了？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"6f0de1f99d","type":"paragraph","text":"柯生（以下简称柯）：同志们到北京大概一个多星期了。他们（指何高、杨光等）来得比较早，一个多月了。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"1c8a06c1c0","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那些同志到过北京吗？","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"043a071f1a","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：没有。他们这一次能见到毛主席，感到非常高兴，对他们是一个很大的鼓舞。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e00e512e01","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：到中国来的同志一共有多少人？","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4f426fc325","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：现在第一批要出发的是330人，后面还有人。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a9d18f5c48","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们来中国多少年了？","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"6942cac326","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：17年了。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"87f0f2e966","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（向柯明）你也来了17年了？","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4856c14691","type":"paragraph","text":"柯明（以下简称明）：我来中国有两年多了。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"b9dd9cb9ee","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：我们在中国17年不能回到缅甸去，这次主席的路线取得了胜利，我们能回去感到非常高兴。（这时主席笑了）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"fe01e87542","type":"paragraph","text":"明：我们在农村坚持了十几年，对毛主席非常敬仰。因为有毛主席，所以我们能坚持下来。请毛主席给我签一个字，留着纪念。（主席在柯明的《毛主席语录》上签字）","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"05220adf64","type":"paragraph","text":"我现在走了。非常感谢主席。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"32093de06a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这不需要感谢。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a3f016e3bf","type":"paragraph","text":"（这时柯明退席）","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"cbd79b4537","type":"paragraph","text":"（向柯生）我跟你见过几次了？","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"51b464ffd1","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：四次。1963年缅甸和谈时一次，最后一次是今年国庆。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f60d048a2e","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：63年到现在已经5年了。那些同志回去都好吗？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9c22663bc3","type":"paragraph","text":"（这时，罗线等四人进来，参加了谈话）","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"061cba85b5","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：很好。这是罗线同志、甘底同志、赵明同志、赵云同志。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"87c72a6739","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（对罗线）你到中国十几年了，一直没有看见你。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"1ee868b994","type":"paragraph","text":"罗线（以下简称罗）：见到主席非常高兴。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"7a4bac5e29","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你一直在四川还是贵州？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a0c68bf1c5","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：住在贵阳。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"8e484c0faa","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：看样子你并不怎么老嘛。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"de6a495264","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：45岁了。还可以打30年仗。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"8ab3f4d957","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：可以。45、55、65、75，可以。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f2da6c72ce","type":"paragraph","text":"重要的是要在斗争中学习，训练班也可以办一点。真正的学习是打仗。如果不去打仗，学习不到什么东西。单是课堂上学军事、学政治我看懂的还是少。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"52cd45af4d","type":"paragraph","text":"你们在中国学习这些东西，回去切不可照抄。要按照你们的情况办。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4bd72f03bd","type":"paragraph","text":"你们跟泰国有接触吗？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"6923eaa1c1","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：跟泰国南部有接触，北部没有。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3d67fe951a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（对罗线）在你们国家，你这个民族算少数民族。你这个民族有多少人？","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a2ab6d2567","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：20万。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d08c04b9e3","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：还有其他少数民族？","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"45b9957156","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：很多，有100多个民族。缅甸人口的45%是少数民族。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4d96975f36","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：少数民族政策是一项重要的政策。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"df0921fee7","type":"paragraph","text":"你们全国有多少人口？","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"fdeacf4718","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：2500万。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"0fa3062e06","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：面积多大？","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d28037ab04","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：262000平方英里。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"176feb3014","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：是一个大国嘛。同越南差不多，比它大一点。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"79c30fe71f","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：比越南大一些。缅甸的面积比罗马尼亚、南斯拉夫、阿尔巴尼亚三个国家加起来还大。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e2d0ce2874","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：26万平方英里，合60万平方公里，跟四川差不多大。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"6cbc4d3470","type":"paragraph","text":"你们都在中国有十几年了吗？","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3c474757c2","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：何高同志17年，杨光同志17年，古方同志15年，罗线同志18年。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3fd3595958","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、邓路线的结果，使我们正是青春的时候在中国度过了，不过为时不晚，还可以打仗。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"233e3d755f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：为时不晚，还可以打仗。你们这个仗是哪一年打起的？","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e1297a6061","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：1948年。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c11594c0c3","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：快20年了。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"6dee09432b","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：明年3月28日就整整20年了。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"968d1eb268","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这是一种情况，是两个帝国主义世界大战之间、处于世界和平时期的一种战争。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"298a6932b7","type":"paragraph","text":"中国的革命你们知道，是第一次世界大战以后才发生的。1918年到1925年7年以后才有北伐战争。1927年蒋介石叛变。共产党跟国民党打仗，是从1927年开始的，一直到第二次世界大战以后。时间拖得很长。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"327364b72d","type":"paragraph","text":"世界上还要打世界大战的。但是你们不能等它。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a2464334dd","type":"paragraph","text":"你们估计奈温有没有可能把外国军队引进来？","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3483554cf1","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：1965年我党主席说过，如果奈温打不过，他可能把美军引进缅甸。我看目前这个可能性不太大。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e0e57878e5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个可能性不太大。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9f93ddcaa9","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：引进美军，我们正希望他这样做。现在看来，美军运到南越很多，要再运到缅甸来有困难。我们得到一个消息，英国人告诉奈温：你不要把希望寄托在美军帮助你们缅甸上。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"de94c73d27","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：但是他们要灭亡的时候，还是要把外国军队引进来的。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"84f5f91c1b","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：对，我们党已经在思想上做好了准备。","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"14b270eedb","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：引进来也不是一件坏事。比如，泰国就驻有美军。有帝国主义，也有封建主义。泰国共产党搞得好，很有前途，很有希望。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f46e6aeb26","type":"paragraph","text":"你们这些同志过去在乡村里的人多，还是在城市里的人多？","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"87f100cdab","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：大部分都是农村的。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a534b5bc9c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：在农村上过学吗？","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9dd18d9518","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：有些上过学。大部分同志到了中国以后才学文化。缅文，景颇文都是到中国以后学习的。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"42157d2d55","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：有这样的教科书吗？","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"daecca4a22","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：用旧的教科书。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d4c591b566","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：也可以自己编嘛。你们的家属、小孩现在教什么？","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3a24611047","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：现在在中国的这些家属，准备将来参加缅甸革命，因此他们现在学习五种东西，即医务、电台、修理枪支、文工团、造炸药。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3c2785ab25","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我说的是小孩。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3d4879585b","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：小孩也学习。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"060381d65c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们是学习缅甸文吗？","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"cdaca6c0cb","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是学习缅甸文。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d073432f56","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：学习缅甸文才好。（对罗线）你们也要学习你们少数民族的文字。你们有自己的书吗？","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"57e9423b4e","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"20aea09020","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们懂不懂缅甸文？","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3f6a073c0b","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：大部分都可以讲缅语。","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d2ae1abeb6","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个条件好。","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"602d34970e","type":"paragraph","text":"他们单独有学校吗？","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"b3911df116","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来（以下简称周）：现在开始单独搞了。","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"50e9e05401","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不是跟我们的孩子们在一起读书？","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a8733996b6","type":"paragraph","text":"周：不是。","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"504025a537","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：在工厂还是在农村？","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c20ca20c34","type":"paragraph","text":"周：有的在农村，有的在工厂。","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c3207fb70a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不是搞了什么工厂吗？","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4ae66448f8","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：大部分在工厂，有一个水银工厂。","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"8ac588777c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个厂子在贵州什么地方？","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3cebb01b82","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：黄平。","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"629307a01d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：是红军经过的地方吗？","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f71d422949","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：是。","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"91820efa8a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那是1934年底，1935年春，那时正是我们很困难的时候，我们党内犯了错误，即王明路线。","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e3533d06ec","type":"paragraph","text":"听说你们党内拥护刘少奇的盛一本集团的几个人都跑掉了？","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"64654f6357","type":"paragraph","text":"康生（以下简称康）：跑了一个。","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"0a13d755ba","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不止跑一个。","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d45ea18ccb","type":"paragraph","text":"康：还有两个没有跑。现在他们叫巴丁-泰路线。一个叫巴丁，另一个叫郭泰。","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"06b8f49ae4","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：在国内有两个，在中国还有一个，即王江。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9182422261","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个名字我熟悉。这个人我见过没有？","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e49bbe396b","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：见过。","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"2ddc96bf90","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他写信给奈温想投降。只要不投降，人数少并不要紧。（问罗线）你过来的时候是多少人？","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"8046042309","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：大概将近400人。","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f5ade1f0c0","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：现在还有多少人？","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3b8adcb9fc","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：347人。","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"77bb49ea02","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：为什么减少了呢？","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d4db4d0114","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有的死亡了，有的回家了。","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"91de550aa3","type":"paragraph","text":"何高：回家的人是这种情况：他们本来是住在中国境内的，后来跑到缅甸参加他们的部队，进入中国后就送他们回家了。","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"33ffa3ad11","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们爱和平，不爱战争。","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f23dafb04d","type":"paragraph","text":"康：现在增加的小孩有多少？","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"299cfd259a","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：480多人，将近500。","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c163154a43","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们回国，你们的家属放心吗？","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"b1f8b55e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：放心。","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"52dd557553","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：放心。我们还准备做一些工作，有条件的、政治好的要动员他们参加缅甸革命。","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"aafd0c587d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：好。要做些工作。缅甸有工业吗？","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"763aaa1613","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：有一点工业。","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"fe1fd7c19c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：有农业、工业、交通、开采石油。","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3c18086515","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是的。","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"ae1dd7febb","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们的同志主要住在哪里？","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"38bfdba63a","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：四川。","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d8adff4129","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：现在集中在什么地方？","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f15441d92a","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：大部分都到怒江坝，靠近保山那个地方。","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"b0bdfa5674","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们到中国十几年了，看样子年纪不很大嘛。","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f35498f4a9","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：赵明同志年纪最轻，今年35岁。赵明同志、赵云同志刚到中国的时候还是小孩。","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d067ce74d5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：35岁，住了17年，到中国时是18岁。","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c519dceaa1","type":"paragraph","text":"你今年四十几岁？","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c44b119dd7","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：45。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9101126718","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（问柯生）你跟他差不多？","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c58068cad1","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：我比他大，今年54。","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"318b46728f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们大部分的困难还是武器和医药。武器你们主要还是向奈温要。","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"86f621069b","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：（对罗线）你要记住一条，向敌人要武器。","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"315c20e515","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：向主席保证。","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"ac002b7deb","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：从敌人手里夺武器，这才有保证。你们有的地方根本没有办法靠外国，如勃固山区。","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"7f3db8ebea","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是的，只能向敌人要。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"5a1271447c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我并不是说，你们向我们要武器我们不给你们。这是个辅助条件。基本的条件要靠你们自己向敌人夺取武器。","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"64df64177e","type":"paragraph","text":"有些武器也可以自己制造，像地雷、手榴弹之类。自己也可办修理厂，修理枪支。","index":140,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"bd47b412e7","type":"paragraph","text":"制造武器、弹药，修理枪支都不困难，这不是一个基本的问题。基本的问题是政治问题。军事不是主要的，政治是主要的。第一条，这个仗要不要打？一个要打，一个不要打。你们现在有那么一些人跑到奈温那里去，他们就是不要打的嘛。过去有这样的人，今后还会有这样的人。","index":141,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"213063ae82","type":"paragraph","text":"第二条，就是群众的问题。依靠群众，还是脱离群众？依靠群众总不会失败的，可以持久。","index":142,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"b3d90a9d02","type":"paragraph","text":"在根据地办学校，要学会政治、学会军事、学会打仗，学会其他的工作。","index":143,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3901967b46","type":"paragraph","text":"他们（指赵明、赵云）来的时候虽然小，那时也有些经验嘛。","index":144,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"dd1352c3a0","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是有一点经验。","index":145,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"1f2144f5f1","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（问罗线）这边是你的部队？","index":146,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"2b9291e48d","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：是的，他们（指赵明等）是快到中国边境时才参加部队的，参加部队3个月以后就到中国境内来了。","index":147,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"945cddb59c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：中国境内也有景颇族嘛。有没有参加你们队伍的？","index":148,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3855574129","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有，现在已经送他们回家了。","index":149,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"7638a3692f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：何必送他们回去呢？你们需要的时候还可以动员一批人参加你的部队。","index":150,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"8cfff40fbe","type":"paragraph","text":"景颇族在中国有多少？","index":151,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"ce8586b3ea","type":"paragraph","text":"周：8万多。","index":152,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"d02696c95a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：都靠近你们边界，可以作为你们的后方嘛。","index":153,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"5657cd13e9","type":"paragraph","text":"缅族跟别的民族有什么联系没有？比如同泰族、同马来亚民族、同印度的民族有没有联系？你们是一个独立的民族？","index":154,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"6d7a13abe6","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：关于缅甸民族的起源还有争论。一种认为缅甸民族是从西藏过去的，另一种认为是从甘肃过去的。缅族处在两大国之间，一个是印度，一个是中国。两国的文化对缅甸都有影响，但是缅族能独立生存下来。缅族跟马来族没有什么关系，跟泰国的泰族经常打仗。","index":155,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"367fc5a4a5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：跟印度的民族有没有什么关系？","index":156,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"cfd6acb7e7","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：也没有。","index":157,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"5389990fd8","type":"paragraph","text":"康：缅语语法跟日语语法一样。","index":158,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"edb8102ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"周：缅文是不是接近藏文？","index":159,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"75ce6eb712","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：跟藏文没有什么关系。","index":160,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"be2274fe82","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：中国民族是从哪里来的，我也搞不清楚。","index":161,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a9a5849e8a","type":"paragraph","text":"周：现在也说法不一，有的认为，北方人是从西北来的，南方广东、福建是从南洋来的。","index":162,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"1c41b8495a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：从两条路来的。","index":163,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"cae8b97a23","type":"paragraph","text":"印度恐怕是从西方来的，看样子就像西方人。那加族的武装呢？","index":164,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"0670258204","type":"paragraph","text":"徐其孝（以下简称徐）：已经出去了。","index":165,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3ddc23b787","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：现在到哪里了？","index":166,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4ad3a39618","type":"paragraph","text":"徐：已经到了江心坡。","index":167,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"0b4e0cf4b2","type":"paragraph","text":"周：他们出去时，护送部队同敌人打了一仗，他们安全过去了。","index":168,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"0a182dc1de","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：带电台了吗？","index":169,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f7544d16fb","type":"paragraph","text":"徐：带了。","index":170,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e36caa0b15","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们也带电台吗？","index":171,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e8c52ca762","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：带了。","index":172,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4021b2efed","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：要带电台。","index":173,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"2b85402b65","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：我们已经准备好了，现在就等下命令了。","index":174,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"33b932f9e4","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：很好。","index":175,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"a2fc8d0f82","type":"paragraph","text":"康：柯生同志他们急着要回去。","index":176,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9c9ea64d72","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：赶快走！赶快走！","index":177,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"08df06fb32","type":"paragraph","text":"康：请柯生同志告诉大家，不会再留他们了。","index":178,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3640d04059","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不会留你们了。我们官僚主义，害得你们等了一个礼拜。","index":179,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"1505d1570c","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：等一个礼拜不要紧。","index":180,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9100c1f565","type":"paragraph","text":"周：最近敌情没有变化。","index":181,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"bc6f3b61f5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们还有什么问题没有？","index":182,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c9d4b46935","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：主要的问题是要回去。","index":183,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e9c27f7414","type":"paragraph","text":"我向主席保证：第一，请主席放心，我们一定要打赢这场战争。第二，要是给我们分配有关国际方面的任务，我们保证完成。","index":184,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f64a4bfd00","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：刚才主席说可以动员中国境内的景颇族参加我们的部队，我非常高兴。我也有这个要求，同志们也有这个要求。","index":185,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"b0054c5007","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你去找，找多少就带多少，找年轻的。","index":186,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"dd2e800b48","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：我很高兴。中国境内的景颇族和缅甸境内的克钦族都是有联系的。","index":187,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"43aa2b5582","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们有义务帮助你们，这是他们的国际主义义务，但是你们要跟他们（指缅共）合作。","index":188,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c328b4c402","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：我们现在已经是缅甸共产党领导下的红军了。","index":189,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"ef458c6866","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那就好。缅族是你们国家的一个大民族，这个民族不解放，你们小民族也不能得到解放。","index":190,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"78bcc1cdfa","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：我们是在缅甸共产党领导下的队伍。","index":191,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"854b854f2c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那就好。","index":192,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"55bd1c45da","type":"paragraph","text":"康：他已经加入共产党了。","index":193,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f55686f359","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那好。","index":194,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"1365926f3d","type":"paragraph","text":"周：最近还通过他去做克钦独立军的工作。","index":195,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"be53dc6a9b","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：克钦独立军有你的部下嘛。","index":196,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"3a5459661e","type":"paragraph","text":"周：有些人过去是他的部下。","index":197,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"1578e3eddf","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：吴努那时非常注意他（罗线）的部队，怕他的部队打回去。你在军队多久？","index":198,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"f3dae999c8","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有二十多年了，从打日本开始就在部队里了。","index":199,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"7ef7fb9676","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：日本是什么时候占领缅甸的？","index":200,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9de4236290","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：1942年占领缅甸，1945年被我们驱逐出去。","index":201,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"c2efc18710","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：1942年到1967年，已经25年了。吴努、奈温这些人是抗日时期开始参加政治活动的？","index":202,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"5009e50639","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：吴努这个人没有参加抗日，他是日本的傀儡，是跟着日本人跑的。过去他访问中国的时候，中国报纸上说他参加过抗日，缅甸同志对这一条就不同意。1945年日本往缅甸南部撤的时候，他一直跟着日本人跑到边境。","index":203,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"4ba83beedb","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这么个人。你刚才讲了两点。","index":204,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"00d78995b2","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：第一点，请主席放心，缅甸共产党一定要用武装夺取政权。第二点，要是给我们国际上的任务，我们保证完成。","index":205,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"0d84c3385d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：什么意思？","index":206,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"9ef732dee4","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：缅甸解放以后，还要支援泰国、马来亚、巴基斯坦、印度、印尼。最近泰共要求我们帮助他们，但那边还没有我们的人，准备派人过去。马共也要求缅共帮助他们送人到马来亚去，现在还做不到。","index":207,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"93cb1f8b1d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：由中国送人去还是由哪里送人去？","index":208,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e711375f46","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：从中国回去，经过缅甸，然后回到马来亚。","index":209,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"e450ca2248","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们的人不多。","index":210,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"b119f9ea5a","type":"paragraph","text":"刘宁一：干部40多人，侨民多一些。","index":211,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"fdb78ad9f1","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：最近几天马来亚有一个示威，因为英镑贬值，群众不满意，发生了示威。","index":212,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"},{"id":"241a723129","type":"paragraph","text":"就谈到这里。","index":213,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674"}],"page":{"id":"dad087ae44","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2dc1f8c674","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}